{
  "stem": "543.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Try-- they try to, to-- the people are-- there are more prisoners there that they try to-- and a lot of people did not do it and meant.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were staying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we find out after a while that the most important thing was to sterilize us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We get other-- a lot of other experiments too, but the most was to sterilize us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they, they tried to give big injections in your womb.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was downstairs where there wasn't like in a-- in a--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Block 10 had three, three, three, three stories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Downstairs was the underside was like a laboratory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big, big-- black, like a [INAUDIBLE], like an [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they could make like an x-ray table.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put a needle in you, and they could see that-- you could follow the-- that fluid, what they put in you, where it came.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, like, they made pictures.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did it downstairs in the building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those needles were very painful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they, they put some burning stuff in it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was blisters and bleeding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were screaming pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no anesthetic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We also had to-- they, they put little pieces out of the womb.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took pieces out of-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pieces out of the womb and they make-- to make it shorter, so you could not expand and could not get children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the one they did only-- the operator did only one, but the needles, I had three.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I have to tell a little story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mostly when you go in Auschwitz, you get so shocked, you don't-- your period disappeared.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the one time I came, I never had my period again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my sister-in-law always did.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
